<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٩٣ ... سُورَةُ الضُّحَى ... آياتها ١١ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالضُّحَى}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِأَوَّلِ النَّهَارِ، أَوْ كُلِّهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَجَى}</span> ... غَطَّى الكَوْنَ بِظَلَامِهِ، وَسَكَنَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا وَدَّعَكَ}</span> ... مَا تَرَكَكَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا قَلَى}</span> ... مَا أَبْغَضَكَ عِنْدَمَا أَبْطَأَ عَلَيْكَ الوَحْيَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَآوَى}</span> ... فَآوَاكَ، وَرَعَاكَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَالًّا}</span> ... لَا تَدْرِي الوَحْيَ، وَلَا تَعْلَمُ القُرْآنَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَائِلًا}</span> ... فَقِيرًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا تَقْهَرْ}</span> ... لَا تُسِئْ مُعَامَلَتَهُ، وَتَاخُذْ مَالَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّائِلَ}</span> ... الفَقِيرَ الَّذِي يَسْأَلُ، وَطَالِبَ العِلْمِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا تَنْهَرْ}</span> ... لَا تَزْجُرْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>